tom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;'><section style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><section style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><section style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><section data-autoskip="1" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><section data-role="outer" label="edit by 135editor" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><section data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="107278" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><section style="margin: 10px auto;outline: 0px;text-align: center;visibility: visible;"><section style="margin-bottom: -12px;margin-left: 6px;outline: 0px;width: 27px;visibility: visible;"><svg version="1.1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" x="0px" y="0px" viewbox="0 0 334.6 286.9" style="visibility: visible;"><polygon style="fill: rgb(245, 202, 70);visibility: visible;" points="334.6,286.9 185.3,286.9 185.3,0.4 334.6,150.4 "></polygon><polygon style="fill: none;stroke: rgb(0, 0, 0);stroke-width: 6;stroke-miterlimit: 10;visibility: visible;" points="147.6,283.9 3.3,283.9 3.3,7.4 147.6,150.4 "></polygon></svg></section><section style="padding-top: 20px;padding-right: 25px;padding-left: 11px;outline: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 253, 244);visibility: visible;text-align: left;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-wrap: wrap;">面对解放军，美国人可谓是</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-wrap: wrap;">“谈之色变”，似乎有解放军在的一天，全世界就充满了威胁，为此，美空军部长做了一个大胆决定。</span></span></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="107278" style='margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;'><section data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="107278" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><section style="margin: 10px auto;outline: 0px;text-align: center;visibility: visible;"><section data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="107278" style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;"><section style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 2em;visibility: visible;"><section style="margin: 10px auto;outline: 0px;line-height: 2em;visibility: visible;"><section style="outline: 0px;display: inline-block;visibility: visible;"><section style="margin: 10px auto;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><section data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="107278" style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;"><section style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 2em;visibility: visible;"><section style="outline: 0px;display: inline-block;visibility: visible;"><section style="margin-left: 1em;outline: 0px;display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;visibility: visible;"><section style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);width: 35px;height: 35px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 35px;background: rgb(68, 117, 241);font-size: 18px;visibility: visible;"><span style='outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 2px;font-size: 17px;font-family: 微软雅黑, "Microsoft YaHei";visibility: visible;'>01</span></section><section style="outline: 0px;flex: 1 1 0%;text-align: left;visibility: visible;"><p draggable="true" style="outline: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 2em;visibility: visible;"><strong style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;"><span style='outline: 0px;font-family: 微软雅黑, "Microsoft YaHei";line-height: 2em;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);text-shadow: none;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;'><strong style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><strong style="outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: Calibri;visibility: visible;"><strong style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"> <strong style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体;visibility: visible;"><strong style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><strong style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">与解放军掰手腕，美军吃了大亏</span></strong></span></strong></span></strong></span></strong></span></strong></strong></span></strong></span></p><section data-width="100%" style="outline: 0px;width: 251.076px;height: 1px;background: rgb(255, 174, 40);overflow: hidden;visibility: visible;"><br data-filtered="filtered" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"></section></section></section></section></section><p style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;"><br></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">最近几年，美军频繁在中国周边试探，南海、台海等地多次出现中美对峙的情况，然而，越来越多的结果表明，美军的图谋终将落空。<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">就围绕台海局势来说，</span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">美智库进行了多次推演，自导自演的最终得出了“美军惨胜”的结论，</span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">但这种推演，忽略了一个重要事实。</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="285" data-backw="554" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100007782" data-ratio="0.5144404332129964" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/PcZfe8Pv6gSMwncc5AP7BY81Eq8cO7wI3SeDw2QPHSicgeNTgbjkr2EiawJT4ov4aXibMybBJ9tScdib4UvMlpEokg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="554" style="width: 100%;height: auto;"></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"><strong><span style="letter-spacing: 2px;font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">在计算解放军空军进入台海时，只考虑到了四代战机或四代半战机</span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);">，</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">要知道，解放军海量的歼</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">-10</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">可发挥的战力，是不容小觑的。</span></span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">所以，我们有理由认为，美智库的推论，其实是“先射箭后画靶”。在后来的实操中，美军明显过于轻“敌”。<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">此前，解放军<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">052D</span>导弹驱逐舰“苏州”舰在台海逼退美加军舰，近距离抵近快速机动，留给美军舰机反应的时间只有<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">10</span>秒。<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">最后，美加军舰不得不悻悻离开，此次对峙，让美军颜面尽失，</span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">复盘之后，美空军部长弗兰克·肯德尔跑到国会，要钱去了。</span></strong></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="377" data-backw="554" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100007781" data-ratio="0.6805054151624549" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/PcZfe8Pv6gSMwncc5AP7BY81Eq8cO7wIoicUibiatX9a7jFDkBVKug0j0bH1d6GwJmbicAJ0KwmbxUQTVxV2eFHWPQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="554" style="width: 100%;height: auto;"></p><section style='margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 2em;visibility: visible;'><section style="margin: 10px auto;outline: 0px;text-align: center;line-height: 2em;"><section style="outline: 0px;display: inline-block;"><section style="margin-left: 1em;outline: 0px;display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;"><section style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);width: 35px;height: 35px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 35px;background: rgb(68, 117, 241);font-size: 18px;"><span style='outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 2px;font-size: 17px;font-family: 微软雅黑, "Microsoft YaHei";'>02</span></section><section style="outline: 0px;flex: 1 1 0%;text-align: left;"><p style="outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 2em;"><strong style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 2em;"><span style='outline: 0px;font-family: 微软雅黑, "Microsoft YaHei";letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 2em;'>  </span><span style='outline: 0px;font-family: 微软雅黑, "Microsoft YaHei";letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 2em;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);'><strong style="outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: Calibri;"><span style="outline: 0px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体;"><strong style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">空军部长倒计时，美军时间不多了</span></strong></span></strong></span></span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></p><section data-width="100%" style="outline: 0px;width: 268.611px;height: 1px;background: rgb(255, 174, 40);overflow: hidden;"> </section></section></section></section></section></section><p style='outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"></span><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;font-family: 宋体;">肯德尔<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">指出，在</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">2025</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">财年，空军部门需要</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">2175</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">亿美元的预算，美空军参谋长和太空作战部长也纷纷点头附和，一致认为，如果国会不能批准预算，那么美国国家安全将受到威胁。</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">钱不到位，那么空军以及太空作战部队将无法做好充足的战斗准备，尤其是在面对强劲对手的情况下，美军的时间真的不多了。<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"><strong><span style="letter-spacing: 2px;font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">这个“对手”，自然说的是中国。</span></strong></span><mpcpc js_editor_cpcad="" class="js_cpc_area res_iframe cpc_iframe" src="/cgi-bin/readtemplate?t=tmpl/cpc_tmpl#1712892437147" data-category_id_list="1|16|17|2|21|24|28|29|31|35|36|37|39|41|42|43|46|47|48|5|50|51|55|56|57|58|59|6|60|61|62|63|64|65|66|67|68|7|8" data-id="1712892437147"></mpcpc><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"><o:p></o:p></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;font-family: 宋体;">肯德尔称，在对抗中国武器方面，美空军已经严重滞后，而导致这一切的源头，就是因为国会批准不痛快，反卫星技术、高超音速武器等现代化武器生产采购计划一直无法推进。</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">他补充道，目前中美正在快速争夺军事技术优势，近来，我们可以明显看到中国空军有了非常明显的现代化进步，对美国构成了前所未有的挑战。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="283" data-backw="553" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100007780" data-ratio="0.5117540687160941" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/PcZfe8Pv6gSMwncc5AP7BY81Eq8cO7wIRuJNnWUVwRrqZISJQ8zejvkZanCP8nfdibghq1iaveDDykrDHFRmlmHQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="553" style="width: 100%;height: auto;"></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">会上，美空军参谋长也大倒苦水，称由于预算不到位，美空军升级战机计划也得延后，<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">F-35A</span>闪电<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">II</span>隐形战斗机和<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">F-15EX</span>鹰<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">II</span>战斗机至今还没买回来。<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">以上种种，导致美国空军机队规模创下几十年来新低。<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">在他们的口中，</span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">似乎国会再不批钱，下一秒中国就打到家门口了</span></strong></span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);">，</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">尤其是肯德尔，直接把话挑明，称中美冲突随时都有可能发生。</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">炒作“中国威胁”争取军费，早已是五角大楼这些军官常用的伎俩，但拿到这些钱，他们真的是用来加固国防了吗？还是另有安排？<o:p></o:p></span></p><section style='margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 2em;visibility: visible;'><section style="margin: 10px auto;outline: 0px;text-align: center;line-height: 2em;"><section style="outline: 0px;display: inline-block;"><section style="margin-left: 1em;outline: 0px;display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;"><section style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);width: 35px;height: 35px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 35px;background: rgb(68, 117, 241);font-size: 18px;"><span style='outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 2px;font-size: 17px;font-family: 微软雅黑, "Microsoft YaHei";'>03</span></section><section style="outline: 0px;flex: 1 1 0%;text-align: left;"><p style="outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 2em;"><strong style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 2em;"><span style='outline: 0px;font-family: 微软雅黑, "Microsoft YaHei";letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 2em;'>       </span><span style='outline: 0px;font-family: 微软雅黑, "Microsoft YaHei";letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 2em;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);'><strong style="outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: Calibri;"><span style="outline: 0px;"><strong style="outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体;"><strong style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">美军的腐败，无药可救</span></strong></span></strong></span></span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></p><section data-width="100%" style="outline: 0px;width: 286.146px;height: 1px;background: rgb(255, 174, 40);overflow: hidden;"><br data-filtered="filtered" style="outline: 0px;"></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style='outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">要知道，美国军费常年稳居全球第一，远远超过了其他国家，如今却再三炒作“中国威胁”，如此不符合常理的逻辑，恐怕美国人看了都觉得可笑。<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">按照肯德尔的说法，由于预算不足，导致美国先进武器研制进度严重落后中国，但根据数据显示，美国新武器资金高的吓人。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="305" data-backw="554" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100007779" data-ratio="0.5505415162454874" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/PcZfe8Pv6gSMwncc5AP7BY81Eq8cO7wIdsicWZ3F7ZjxibvqeiaiaZC1iaUIuMScGCarqPDMZEMMicRPTX6HwZ2o0HpA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="554" style="width: 100%;height: auto;"></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">此前，美政府就有审计报告显示，美国的军费管理过于混乱，大批资金流向不明，甚至存在各种夸张的虚列名目。<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">比如，在<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">2016</span>年，美国空军有一笔<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">32.6</span>万美元的支出，而如此巨额的资金，并非用于研发新武器，也不是用于装备采购，而是用来买咖啡杯。<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"><strong><span style="letter-spacing: 2px;font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">32.6<span style="letter-spacing: 2px;font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">万美元</span></span></strong><strong><span style="letter-spacing: 2px;font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"><span style="letter-spacing: 2px;font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">一共买回来</span><span style="letter-spacing: 2px;font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">391</span><span style="letter-spacing: 2px;font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">个咖啡杯，平均一个杯子的单价高达</span><span style="letter-spacing: 2px;font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">826</span><span style="letter-spacing: 2px;font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">美元。</span></span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"><o:p></o:p></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">同年，五角大楼总监察长办公室就发布报告表示，美军有</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;">6.5</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">万亿美元不知道用在何处，去向不明。</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">而针对美国军队的财务审计工作，更是</span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">连续</span>6<span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">年失败</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">，负责审计工作的会计师事务所最终给出“拒绝表示意见”的结论，这意味着什么呢？</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="433" data-backw="554" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100007778" data-ratio="0.7815884476534296" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/PcZfe8Pv6gSMwncc5AP7BY81Eq8cO7wIA7RKeHUaek5WYw7ZJleL56MEdzocekHHkNIs1Qj508IwibcQ0VCibFDg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="554" style="width: 100%;height: auto;"></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">这是一个比较专业的会计用语，大白话说就是，</span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">你的账目太糟糕了，里面存在大量漏洞和欺诈，改都没法改。</span></strong></span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;"><o:p></o:p></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">事实上，美军贪污腐败问题，根本没法管，根本原因是“枪指挥党”带来的弊端。有网友评价称，没有威胁论，哪有军工复合体的分肥，哪有好战分子挣钱的机会呢？<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">相比之下，解放军有着很大不同。</span></span><mpcpc js_editor_cpcad="" class="js_cpc_area res_iframe cpc_iframe" src="/cgi-bin/readtemplate?t=tmpl/cpc_tmpl#1712892429306" data-category_id_list="1|16|17|2|21|24|28|29|31|35|36|37|39|41|42|43|46|47|48|5|50|51|55|56|57|58|59|6|60|61|62|63|64|65|66|67|68|7|8" data-id="1712892429306"></mpcpc><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: Calibri;"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><section style='margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 2em;visibility: visible;'><section style="margin: 10px auto;outline: 0px;text-align: center;line-height: 2em;"><section style="outline: 0px;display: inline-block;"><section style="margin-left: 1em;outline: 0px;display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;"><section style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);width: 35px;height: 35px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 35px;background: rgb(68, 117, 241);font-size: 18px;"><span style='outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 2px;font-size: 17px;font-family: 微软雅黑, "Microsoft YaHei";'>04</span></section><section style="outline: 0px;flex: 1 1 0%;text-align: left;"><p style="outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 2em;"><strong style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 2em;"><span style='outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 2em;font-family: 微软雅黑, "Microsoft YaHei";'>       </span><span style='outline: 0px;font-family: 微软雅黑, "Microsoft YaHei";letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 2em;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);'><strong style="outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: Calibri;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 宋体;"><strong style="outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;"><strong style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">中国国防部有言在先</span></strong></span></strong></span></span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span></p><section data-width="100%" style="outline: 0px;width: 286.146px;height: 1px;background: rgb(255, 174, 40);overflow: hidden;"><br data-filtered="filtered" style="outline: 0px;"></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style='outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">首先，中方的国防政策一向以防御为主，面对美军再三炒作的“中国威胁论”，我国国防部发言人曾表示，我们坚决反对有关国家以“中国军事威胁”争取军费。<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">从始至终，中国都是世界和平的建设者、全球发展的贡献者、国际秩序的维护者。</span><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">对于世界各国而言，中国是新时代发展难得的机遇，而不是“谈之色变”的威胁、挑战。</span></strong></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="344" data-backw="553" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100007777" data-ratio="0.6220614828209765" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/PcZfe8Pv6gSMwncc5AP7BY81Eq8cO7wInSVc4009RjSib2RXBY0GB9W4FePUOib5IjVibH4EBkx7lCqs221m2Cnsw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="553" style="width: 100%;height: auto;"></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">美国的军费已经够多了，维护国家安全绰绰有余，但他们却以此四处发动战争，策划“颜革”，在全世界制造动乱。<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 2px;">如今的巴以冲突、俄乌冲突，就是美军祸乱全球最典型的例子，身为世界第一大国，本应负担起更多的国际责任和义务，基于道义和全球利益展开外交工作。<o:p></o:p></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 2px;font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;">显然，世界之所以战火不断，美国难辞其咎，但时代的列车已经转向，维护霸权早已是逆时代之行为，美国若不及时掉头，或将被整个世界抛弃。</span><span style="letter-spacing: 2px;font-family: Calibri;font-size: 10.5pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p><br></p><p style="display: none;"><mp-style-type data-value="3"></mp-style-type></p></div>          <script type="text/javascript" nonce="2026110680" reportloaderror>            var first_sceen__time = (+new Date());            if ("" == 1 && document.getElementById('js_content')) {              document.getElementById('js_content').addEventListener("selectstart",function(e){ e.preventDefault(); });            }          </script>        </div>                        <div id="js_tags_preview_toast" class="article-tag__error-tips" style="display: none;">预览时标签不可点</div>                        <div id="content_bottom_area" class="rich_media_tool_area"></div>                              </div>    </div>]]></description>
